(OOC: I'm back everyone!! *_*)

Teltoli raised an eyebrow when he was talking about knocking 
Carnage's head off and then telling her Good Day. She slanted a look 
at Carnage and crossed her eyes, making a discreet 'He's crazy!' 
sign. She then stifled a smirk.

"Good Day? Well that really depends on your point of view" She said 
sarcastically, and out of the corner of her eye, she saw Sabre (the 
bald eagle) sitting on the branch directly above Instrat, lifting his 
tail slightly. Her eyes brightened, but no one else noticed. 

If eagles could look mischevious, Sabre would have right then. He 
aimed perfectly, and dropped his 'poop missile' on straight perfect 
aim towards the bots head, impossible to miss. 

The Fuzor kept her wrist dart aimed on Instrat's head, waiting for 
the bot to make a move.
